trans-unit.source: Defines the template of the final step for creating a user account with the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Define o modelo da etapa final para a criação de uma conta de usuário com o controle <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> class is derived from <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatedWizardStep> and used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> control.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> classe é derivada de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatedWizardStep> e usado pelo <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> controle.

trans-unit.source: By default the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> step is displayed after the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizardStep> step.
trans-unit.target: Por padrão o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> etapa é exibida após o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizardStep> etapa.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> step is a required step of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> control.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> etapa é uma etapa necessária do <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> controle.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the type of user interface (UI) to display for the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep" /> page of a <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o tipo de interface do usuário (IU) a ser exibida para a página <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep" /> de um controle <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="F:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType.Complete" /> enumeration value for the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType" /> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="F:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType.Complete" /> valor de enumeração para o <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType" /> enumeração.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType%2A> property specifies the type of navigation UI to display for the final user account creation step (the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizardStep> step) of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> control.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType%2A> propriedade especifica o tipo de navegação da interface do usuário a ser exibida para a etapa de criação de conta de usuário final (o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizardStep> etapa) da <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard> controle.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType%2A> property overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepBase.StepType%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property to ensure that <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> is always set to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType.Complete> value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType> enumeration.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType%2A> substituições de propriedade a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepBase.StepType%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> propriedade para garantir que <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep> é sempre definido como o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType.Complete> valor o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WizardStepType> enumeração.

trans-unit.source: Attempting to set the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType%2A> property to a different value will result in an <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.
trans-unit.target: Tentativa de definir o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType%2A> propriedade para um valor diferente resultará em um <xref:System.InvalidOperationException>.

trans-unit.source: This property cannot be set by themes or style sheet themes.
trans-unit.target: Essa propriedade não pode ser definida por temas ou temas de folha de estilo.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeableAttribute> and [ASP.NET Themes and Skins](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/5df3ebbd-d46c-4502-9406-02f9df4ef2c3).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeableAttribute> e [capas e temas do ASP.NET](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/5df3ebbd-d46c-4502-9406-02f9df4ef2c3).

trans-unit.source: An attempt was made to set the <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType" /> property.
trans-unit.target: Foi feita uma tentativa de definir a propriedade <see cref="P:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CompleteWizardStep.StepType" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the title to display for the final user account creation step of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Obtém ou define o título a ser exibido para a etapa de criação de conta do usuário final do controle <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" />.

trans-unit.source: The title to use for the final user account creation step of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> control.
trans-unit.target: O título a ser usado para a etapa de criação de conta do usuário final do <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.CreateUserWizard" /> controle.

trans-unit.source: The value of this property, when set, can be saved automatically to a resource file by using a designer tool.
trans-unit.target: O valor dessa propriedade, quando definido, podem ser salvos automaticamente em um arquivo de recurso usando uma ferramenta de designer.

trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte <xref:System.ComponentModel.LocalizableAttribute> e [globalização e localização](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/8ef3838e-9d05-4236-9dd0-ceecff9df80d).
